    "description": "Xpressbees International Enterprises, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Digital Marketing Manager for our Vijayawada operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Xpressbees International Enterprises:\nXpressbees International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Learning & development budget\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Xpressbees International Enterprises!",
